headline: Home Depot Tops Q4 Earnings Estimates, Stock Dips on Sales Miss
summary: HD Q4 EPS tops estimates, but sales miss and margin pressures weigh. Management's FY26 outlook calls for modest sales and EPS growth and a flat to 2% rise in comps.
